ump%20Organization%20in%202021%2C%20speaking%20with%20the%20media%20and%20providing%20crucial%20financial%20documents%20that%20led%20to%20her%20former%20father-in-law's%20eventual%20conviction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20that%20time%2C%20she%20was%20also%20battling%20an%20eviction%20order%20for%20her%20Upper%20West%20Side%20apartment%2C%20which%20Allen%20Weisselberg%20had%20arranged%20for%20her%20after%20her%202018%20divorce%20from%20his%20son%2C%20Barry%20Weisselberg.%20The%20couple%20was%20also%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20custody%20battle%2C%20she%20told%20The%20Nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20their%20divorce%2C%20Jennifer%20Weisselberg%20and%20her%20ex-husband%20lived%20for%2010%20years%20rent-free%20in%20a%20glamorous%20Central%20Park%20South%20apartment%20provided%20to%20them%20as%20an%20untaxed%20perk%20from%20the%20Trump%20Organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20were%20friendly%20with%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20who%20invited%20them%20to%20his%202017%20inauguration%20and%20also%20signed%20some%20of%20the%20Weisselberg's%20kids'%20tuition%20checks%20%E2%80%94%20further%20evidence%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmanhattan-da-trump-signed-tuition-checks-allen-weisselberg-kids-2021-7%23%3A~%3Atext%3DProsecutors%2520said%2520that%2520from%25202012%2Caccount%2520of%2520the%2520Donald%2520J%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20untaxed%20compensation%20normalized%20within%20the%20Trump%20Organization%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20prosecutors%20said%20in%20Allen%20Weisselberg's%20indictment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20Barry%20Weisselberg%20filed%20for%20divorce%2C%20his%20father%20put%20Jennifer%20Weisselberg%20up%20in%20a%20new%20apartment%20managed%20by%20a%20real%20estate%20magnate%20known%20to%20for%20its%20frequent%20evictions%2C%20The%20Nation%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Weisselberg%20acknowledged%20that%20she%20struggled%20to%20make%20the%20%246%2C050%20rent%20in%20the%20new%20place%2C%20especially%20be