0Weisselberg%20has%20been%20battling%20Barry%20for%20custody%20of%20the%20couple's%20two%20teenagers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Weisselberg%20previously%20sought%20and%20won%20a%20domestic%20violence%20protection%20order%20against%20Barry%20Weisselberg%2C%20though%20it%20was%20later%20vacated%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20took%20physical%20custody%20of%20the%20kids%20in%20February%202020%20before%20she%20began%20cooperating%20with%20lawyers.%20A%20psychiatrist%20ordered%20to%20evaluate%20Jennifer%20Weisselberg%20before%20Barry%20took%20the%20kids%20found%20her%20to%20%26quot%3Bmanic%20psychotic%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20report%2C%20per%20The%20Nation.%20She%20told%20the%20outlet%20she%20was%20taken%20but%20not%20admitted%20to%20Bellevue%20Hospital%20in%20Manhattan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20since%20lost%20all%20custody%20and%20visitation%20rights%20with%20her%20kids%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20her%20home%2C%20the%20outlet%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20is%20no%20evident%20proof%20that%20Jennifer%20Weisselberg's%20bad%20luck%20is%20retaliation%20for%20her%20cooperation%20in%20the%20case%20against%20the%20Trump%20Organization%2C%20an%20unnamed%20official%20who%20worked%20in%20the%20Manhattan%20DA's%20office%20with%20Jennifer%20Weisselberg%20on%20the%20cases%20involving%20Allen%20Weisselberg%20and%20the%20Trump%20Org%20told%20The%20Nation%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20credible%20that%20they're%20retaliating%20against%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20also%20acknowledging%20that%20Jennifer%20Weisselberg%20may%20have%20been%20the%20harbinger%20of%20her%20own%20bad%20luck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Weisselberg%20told%20The%20Nation%20she%20believed%20speaking%20out%20against%20the%20Trump%20Organization%20would%20help%20her%20get%20her%20kids%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20she%20is%20still%20searching%20for%20a%20permanent%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%