e.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20Netaji%20(Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav)%2C%20Sharad%20Yadav%2C%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%2C%20and%20parties%20from%20South%20India%20raised%20the%20demand%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20the%20Congress%20refused%20to%20do%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20do%20they%20want%20to%20conduct%20caste%20census%20today%3F%20Because%20they%20know%20that%20their%20traditional%20vote%20bank%20is%20not%20with%20them.%20But%20the%20backward%20classes%2C%20Dalit%2C%20and%20adivasis%20know%20that%20they%20had%20betrayed%20them%20after%20Independence%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yadav%20has%20been%20training%20his%20guns%20at%20the%20Congress%20lately%20and%20has%20also%20claimed%20that%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20does%20not%20want%20to%20ally%20with%20his%20outfit%20after%20their%20relations%20soured%20over%20seat-sharing%20for%20the%20November%2017%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20he%20said%20the%20Congress%20did%20not%20implement%20the%20Mandal%20Commission%20recommendations%20and%20had%20opposed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-stopped-caste-census-the-congress-akhilesh-yadav-in-madhya-pradesh-4562026%5C%22%3Ecaste%20census%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20another%20instance%2C%20he%20told%20a%20rally%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20that%20neither%20Congress%20nor%20BJP%20have%20done%20anything%20for%20the%20poor%20and%20farmers%20when%20they%20were%20in%20power%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20poster%20war%20had%20also%20erupted%20between%20the%20two%20parties%20after%20a%20poster%20claiming%20Mr%20Yadav%20as%20the%20country's%20%26quot%3Bfuture%20prime%20minister%26quot%3B%20was%20put%20up%20outside%20a%20Samajwadi%20Party%20office.%20Soon%20after%2C%20a%20similar%20poster%20describing%20Mr%20Gandhi%20as%20the%20'2024%20prime%20minister'%20surfaced%20outside%20a%20Congress%20office%20in%20Lucknow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20despite%20the%20