o%20pay%20homage%20to%20the%20cultural%20significance%20of%20the%20song%20while%20adhering%20to%20the%20terms%20outlined%20in%20the%20agreement%2C%20which%20permitted%20them%20to%20use%20the%20lyrics%20with%20a%20new%20composition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20understand%20the%20emotional%20attachment%20that%20audiences%20may%20have%20to%20the%20original%20composition%2C%20and%20while%20all%20art%20is%20inherently%20subjective%20if%20our%20interpretation%20has%20hurt%20sentiments%20or%20caused%20unintended%20distress%2C%20we%20offer%20our%20sincere%20apologies%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProduced%20by%20Ronnie%20Screwvala%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20RSVP%20Movies%20and%20Siddharth%20Roy%20Kapur's%20Roy%20Kapur%20Films%2C%20and%20directed%20by%20Raja%20Krishna%20Menon%2C%20the%20film%20features%20Ishaan%2C%20Mrunal%20Thakur%2C%20Priyanshu%20Painyuli%20and%20Soni%20Razdan%20in%20pivotal%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20the%20book%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Burning%20Chaffees%20%3C%2Fem%3Eby%20Brigadier%20Balram%20Singh%20Mehta%2C%20the%20film%20is%20written%20by%20Menon%2C%20Tanmay%20Mohan%2C%20and%20Ravinder%20Randhawa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20title%20of%20the%20film%20is%20a%20tribute%20to%20the%20amphibious%20war%20tank%20called%20the%20PT-76%20(Palavushi%20Tanka)%2C%20popularly%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BPippa%2C%26quot%3B%20akin%20to%20an%20empty%20tin%20of%20ghee%20that%20smoothly%20floats%20on%20water.%20This%20wartime%20saga%20narrates%20a%20story%20of%20patriotism%20and%20traces%20the%20coming%20of%20age%20of%20Captain%20Balram%20Mehta%20(essayed%20by%20Ishaan)%20of%20the%2045%20Cavalry%20Tank%20Squadron.%20Together%2C%20Balram%20Mehta%20and%20the%20Indian%20Armed%20Forces%20exemplify%20valour%20and%20courage%2C%20in%20a%20war%20for%20the%20liberation%20of%20another%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film%20is%20streaming%20on%20the%20OTT%20platform%20Amazon%20Prime%20Video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci