20for%20girls%2C%20about%20the%20Jandhan%20Yojana%2C%20the%20financial%20inclusion%2C%20about%20building%20houses%2C%20the%20Awas%20Yojana...And%20these%20other%20campaigns...Digital%20India%20campaign...the%20Startup%20India%20campaign%2C%20the%20Skill%20India%20campaign...it%20is%20when%20you%20connect%20these%20dots%2C%20it's%20really%20when%20you%20see%20the%20cumulative%20impact%20of%20all%20of%20this%20on%20the%20lives%20of%20people%2C%20that%20is%20the%20change%20which%20is%20underway%20in%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20EAM%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20also%20reflected%20on%20the%20comprehensive%20changes%20witnessed%20in%20the%20past%20ten%20years%2C%20noting%20that%20the%20government%2C%20nearing%20the%20completion%20of%20its%20second%20term%20next%20year%2C%20has%20created%20almost%20as%20many%20new%20universities%20and%20colleges%20as%20the%20country%20had%20in%20the%20previous%2065%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20when%20we%20look%20at%20the%20last%20ten%20years%2C%20because%20by%20next%20year%20the%20government%20would%20be%20completing%20its%20second%20term.%20These%20ten%20years%20have%20actually%20been%20a%20socioeconomic%20revolution%20in%20India...we%20have%20actually%20created%20almost%20as%20many%20new%20universities%20and%20colleges%20in%20the%20last%20ten%20years%20as%20the%20country%20had%20in%20the%20previous%2065%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20evolving%20India-UK%20relationship%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20expressed%20the%20need%20to%20reframe%20the%20partnership%20in%20light%20of%20the%20profound%20changes%20in%20both%20nations.%20He%20emphasised%20the%20importance%20of%20preparing%20for%20a%20contemporary%20era%20and%20exploring%20new%20convergences%20to%20unlock%20the%20unrealized%20potential%20between%20India%20and%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20today%20trying%20to%20reframe%20the%20relationship%20between%20India%20and%20the%20UK.%20We%20are%20trying%20to%20do%20so%20because%2C%20in%20the%20last%20many%20decades%2C%20our%20two%20countries%20have%20each%20changed%20profoundly.%20We%20have%20changed%20in%20ourselves%2C%20our%20relationships%2C%20our%20linkages%20and%20approaches%20to%20the%20world%3B%20therefore%2C%20it%20is%20important%20that%20we%20prepare%20a%20partnership%20for%20a%20contemporary%20era%20in%20which%20we%20look%20to%20explore%20new%20convergences%20to%20see%20if%20there%20is%20unrealistic%20potential%20out%20there...%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Jaishankar.%3Cbr%3E%5CnEAM%20Jaishankar%20arrived%20in%20Britain%20on%20Saturday%20and%20will%20conclude%20his%20visit%20on%20November%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20the%20UK%20have%20a%20%26quot%3Bgrowing%20bilateral%20partnership%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20MEA%20stated%20in%20a%20release%20earlier%2C%20noting%20that%20the%20two%20countries%20launched%20a%20Comprehensive%20Strategic%20Partnership%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20and%20the%20UK%20share%20a%20warm%20and%20thriving%20relationship.%20The%20India-UK%20Comprehensive%20Strategic%20Partnership%20was%20launched%20in%202021%20along%20with%20the%20India-UK%20Roadmap%202030%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20MEA%20stated%20in%20its%20release.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BThe%20Roadmap%20is%20a%20commitment%20to%20a%20partnership%20that%20delivers%20for%20both%20countries.%20EAM's%20visit%20will%20give%20new%20impetus%20to%20the%20friendly%20ties%20between%20the%20two%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESignificantly%2C%20India%20and%20the%20UK%20are%20negotiating%20a%20Free%20Trade%20Agreement%20(FTA).%20Talks%20for%20FTA%20between%20India%20and%20the%20UK%20started%20in%202022%20and%20the%2012th%20round%20of%20negotiations%20took%20place%20from%20August%208-31%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22publ