during%20the%20pandemic...%20we%20have%20schemes%20for%20everyone.%20There%20is%20no%20one%20who%20can%20claim%20that%20they%20lost%20anything%20in%20five%20years%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20swept%20out%20the%20BJP%20government%20of%20Raman%20Singh%20in%202018%2C%20winning%2068%20out%20of%20the%2090%20assembly%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20Congress%20currently%20holds%2071%20seats%20in%20the%20House%20following%20bypoll%20victories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Baghel%2C%20who%20re-built%20the%20party%20in%20the%20state%20after%20the%202013%20Jhiram%20Ghati%20Maoist%20attack%2C%20was%20credited%20with%20the%20victory.%20He%20was%20picked%20for%20the%20top%20job%20by%20the%20party's%20top%20leadership%20above%20three%20other%20contenders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20appeared%20confident%20that%20the%20people%20will%20give%20the%20party%20another%20chance%20in%20view%20of%20its%20governance%20of%20the%20last%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20trust%20only%20the%20Congress%2C%20its%20guarantee.%20Neither%20they%20buy%20the%20guarantees%20of%20Raman%20Singh%20or%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20citing%20several%20promises%20made%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20he%20said%2C%20has%20kept%20its%20word%20at%20every%20instance%2C%20including%20the%20loan%20waiver%20for%20farmers.%20%26quot%3BRahul%20Gandhi%20had%20said%20it%20would%20be%20done%20in%2010%20days.%20We%20did%20it%20within%20two%20hours%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20halved%20the%20electricity%20bills%2C%20bought%20tendu%20leaves%20at%20Rs%204000%20for%20each%2050%20kg%20bag%2C%20gave%20each%20family%2035%20kilos%20of%20vegetables...%20so%20people%20trust%20the%20Congress%20guarantee%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20what%20can%20he%20offer%20the%20people%20this%20time%2C%20he%20said%20the%20party%20has%20spoken%20of%20wai