0if%20they%20commit%20to%20eventually%20building%20them%20in%20India%2C%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20final%20decision%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20taken%20on%20the%20policy's%20contours%2C%20the%20people%20said%2C%20asking%20not%20to%20be%20identified%20as%20the%20discussions%20are%20private.%20Spokespeople%20from%20India's%20heavy%20industries%20and%20commerce%20ministries%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20emails%20seeking%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20the%20Austin-based%20EV%20manufacturer%20had%20sought%20duty%20cuts%20on%20import%20of%20electric%20vehicles.%20It%20was%20hoping%20to%20have%20the%20rates%20reduced%20to%2040%25%20from%20the%20current%20range%20of%2070%25-100%25%20for%20its%20vehicles%2C%20depending%20on%20their%20import%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETesla's%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20Elon%20Musk%20is%20likely%20to%20meet%20Trade%20Minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%20later%20this%20week%20to%20discuss%20the%20company's%20plans%20to%20set%20up%20a%20factory%20in%20the%20South%20Asian%20nation.%20Mr%20Goyal%20is%20in%20San%20Francisco%20to%20attend%20the%20ministerial%20engagements%20of%20Indo-Pacific%20Economic%20Framework%20and%20the%20Asia-Pacific%20Economic%20Cooperation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETesla%20is%20seeking%20to%20break%20into%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20promising%20auto%20markets%20where%20the%20demand%20for%20electric%20vehicles%20is%20rising%20among%20the%20country's%20burgeoning%20middle%20class.%20For%20India%2C%20Tesla's%20investment%20would%20aid%20the%20government's%20push%20to%20increase%20the%20share%20of%20manufacturing%20in%20the%20nation's%20GDP%20while%20also%20creating%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20electric%20car%20market%20is%20currently%20at%20a%20nascent%20stage%20with%20EVs%20accounting%20for%20just%201.3%25%20of%20the%20total%20passenger%20vehicles%20sold%20last%20year%2C%20according%20to%20BloombergNEF.%20The%20adoption%20of%20EVs%20in%20the%20cou