sports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fwe-talk-about-kohli-babar-but-wasim-akrams-ultimate-praise-for-rohit-sharma-4569910%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%201962%20Ferrari%20Is%202nd%20Most%20Expensive%20Car%20Ever%20Auctioned.%20It%20Sold%20For...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%201962%20Ferrari%20250%20GTO%20sports%20car%20sold%20for%20%2451.7%20million%20in%20New%20York%20on%20Monday%2C%20making%20it%20the%20second%20most%20expensive%20car%20ever%20sold%20at%20auction%2C%20Sotheby's%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bright%20red%20roadster%20had%20been%20the%20property%20of%20an%20American%20collector%20for%20the%20past%2038%20years%2C%20and%20its%20auction%20price%20was%20surpassed%20only%20by%20that%20of%20a%20Mercedes%20300%20SLR%20Uhlenhaut%20Coupe%20that%20went%20for%20135%20million%20euros%20in%202022%2C%20the%20auction%20house%20said.%20That%20would%20be%20%24144%20million%20at%20today's%20exchange%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20250%20GTO%20went%20on%20sale%20Monday%20evening%20after%20a%20few%20minutes%20of%20bidding%20in%20the%20auction%20room%2C%20but%20at%20a%20price%20lower%20than%20the%20more%20than%20%2460%20million%20expected%20by%20RM%20Sotheby's%2C%20the%20luxury%20car%20subsidiary%20of%20the%20auction%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESotheby's%20did%20not%20identify%20the%20winning%20bidder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDating%20from%201962%2C%20this%20legendary%20Scuderia%20sports%20car%20--%20chassis%203765%2C%20four-liter%20engine%20developing%20390%20horsepower%20--%20had%20finished%20second%20in%20a%201%2C000%20km%20endurance%20race%20on%20the%20German%20Nurburgring%20circuit%2C%20as%20well%20as%20in%20the%20legendary%2024%20Hours%20of%20Le%20Mans%2C%20where%20the%20team%20had%20to%20withdraw%20due%20to%20engine%20failure%2C%20according%20to%20RM%20Sotheby's.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20several%20years%20of%20competition%20on%20the%20Italian%20mainland%20and%20in%20Sicily%2C%20the%20car%20was%20sold%20and%20exported%20to%20the%20US%20in%20the%20late%201960s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERestored%20and%20modified%2C%20the%20250%20GTO%20changed%20American%20owners%20several%20times%20before%20ending%20up%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20an%20Ohio%20%26quot%3Bdedicated%20collector%26quot%3B%20in%201985%2C%20who%20sold%20it%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20stunning%20GTO%20offers%20its%20next%20caretaker%20further%20touring%20and%20vintage%20racing%20enjoyment%2C%20or%20display%20at%20major%20concours%20d'elegance%20and%20marque%20gatherings%20worldwide%2C%26quot%3B%20Sotheby's%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mercedes%20300%20SLR%20Uhlenhaut%20Coupe%20that%20fetched%20135%20million%20euros%20in%202022%20was%20one%20of%20only%20two%20examples%20of%20the%20sport%20car.%20It%20sold%20at%20a%20confidential%20auction%20at%20the%20German%20manufacturer's%20museum%20in%20Stuttgart%20and%20was%20the%20most%20expensive%20car%20ever%20sold%20worldwide%2C%20whether%20at%20auction%20or%20privately%2C%20a%20RM%20Sotheby's%20spokesman%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20week%2C%20New%20York%20auction%20houses%20Sotheby's%20and%20Christie's%20conclude%20their%20autumn%20season%20of%20art%20sales%2C%20which%20have%20not%20been%20affected%20by%20hard%20times%20and%20are%20raking%20in%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20market%20is%20driven%20by%20China%20and%20Asia%20and%20shows%20no%20signs%20of%20slowing%20down%2C%20according%20to%20Sotheby's%2C%20despite%20a%20tense%20international%20context.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhatever%20happens%20in%20the%20financial%20markets%2C%20a%20car%20of%20this%20caliber%20is%20a%20collector's%20item%2C%20a%20once-in-a-lifetime%20opportunity%2C%26quot%3B%20Michael%20Caimano%20of%20RM%20Sotheby's%20told%20AFP%20before%20the%20sale%2C%20comparing%20the%20Ferrari%20to%20a%20work%20of%20art%20that%20%26quot%3Bcan%20be%20touched%2C%20felt%20and%20heard.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%2