Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20other%20members%20of%20the%20federal%20judiciary%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20nine%20life-tenured%20justices%20had%20long%20acted%20with%20no%20binding%20ethics%20code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20absence%2C%20the%20statement%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bhas%20led%20in%20recent%20years%20to%20the%20misunderstanding%20that%20the%20justices%20of%20this%20court%2C%20unlike%20all%20other%20jurists%20in%20this%20country%2C%20regard%20themselves%20as%20unrestricted%20by%20any%20ethics%20rules.%20To%20dispel%20this%20misunderstanding%2C%20we%20are%20issuing%20this%20code%2C%20which%20largely%20represents%20a%20codification%20of%20principles%20that%20we%20have%20long%20regarded%20as%20governing%20our%20conduct.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20has%20been%20buffeted%20for%20months%20by%20revelations%20regarding%20justices%20over%20undisclosed%20trips%20on%20private%20jets%2C%20luxury%20vacations%2C%20real%20estate%20and%20recreational%20vehicle%20deals%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20had%20become%20an%20political%20flashpoint%2C%20with%20Democrats%20in%20Congress%20calling%20on%20the%20court%20to%20adopt%20an%20ethics%20code%2C%20while%20many%20Republicans%20viewed%20the%20ethics%20narrative%20involving%20the%20court%20as%20cooked%20up%20by%20liberals%20upset%20at%20its%20rightward%20leanings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ethics%20drum%20beat%20added%20pressure%20to%20a%20court%20already%20facing%20declining%20public%20approval%20following%20major%20rulings%20in%20its%20past%20two%20terms%20powered%20by%20its%20conservative%20majority.%20The%20court%20ended%20its%20recognition%20of%20a%20constitutional%20right%20to%20abortion%2C%20expanded%20gun%20rights%20and%20rejected%20affirmative%20action%20collegiate%20admissions%20policies%20often%20used%20to%20increase%20Black%20and%20Hispanic%20student%20enrollment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20ethics%20revelations%20in%20recent%20months%20involved%20Justice%20Clarence%20Thomas%2C%20one%20of%20the%20court's%20most%20conservative%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20outlet%20ProPublica%20has%20detailed%20luxury%20trips%20taken%20for%20years%20by%20Thomas%20provided%20by%20Texas%20businessman%20Harlan%20Crow%20as%20well%20as%20real%20estate%20transactions%20involving%20the%20justice%20and%20the%20billionaire%20Republican%20donor.%20ProPublica%20also%20reported%20that%20the%20conservative%20Koch%20network%20of%20political%20donors%2C%20which%20has%20had%20multiple%20cases%20before%20the%20court%2C%20has%20brought%20Thomas%20in%20recent%20years%20to%20its%20summit%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20report%20by%20Senate%20Democrats%20in%20October%20also%20found%20that%20Thomas%20apparently%20failed%20to%20repay%20at%20least%20a%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20portion%26quot%3B%20of%20a%20%24267%2C230%20loan%20he%20received%20from%20longtime%20friend%20Anthony%20Welters%20to%20buy%20a%20luxury%20motor%20coach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699928940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-06%2Fus-supreme-court-650-reuters_650x400_61498490054.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-supreme-court-adopts-its-first-formal-ethics-code-for-judges-4572044%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Monday%20adopted%20its%20first%20formal%20code%20of%20conduct%20governing%20the%20ethical%20behavior%20of%20its%20nine%20justices%2C%20bowing%20to%20months%20of%20outside%20pressure%20over%20revelations%20of%20undisclosed%20luxury%20trips%20and%20hobnobbing%20with%20wealthy%20benefactors.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-supreme-court-adopts-its-first-formal-ethics-code-for-judges-4572044%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3