s%20posed%20by%20their%20demanding%20careers%20and%20highlighted%20the%20need%20to%20prioritize%20'quality'%20time%20together.%20Deepika%20also%20attributed%20her%20success%20to%20her%20strong%20work%20ethic%20and%20being%20protective%20of%20what%20she%20has%20built.%20On%20the%20professional%20front%2C%20she%20has%20upcoming%20films%20with%20her%20husband%20and%20other%20interesting%20projects%20in%20the%20pipeline.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fdeepika-padukone-emphasizes-the-importance-of-quality-time-in-marriage-with-ranveer-singh%2Farticleshow%2F105195761.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMy%20Hope%20And%20Expectation...%26quot%3B%3A%20Biden's%20Call%20For%20Protecting%20Gaza%20Hospital%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20urged%20Israel%20on%20Monday%20to%20protect%20Gaza's%20main%20hospital%20as%20heavy%20fighting%20between%20Israeli%20forces%20and%20Hamas%20raged%20around%20the%20complex.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20my%20hope%20and%20expectation%20that%20there%20will%20be%20less%20intrusive%20action%20relative%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%20told%20reporters%20in%20the%20Oval%20Office%20when%20asked%20if%20he%20had%20expressed%20concerns%20to%20Israel%20on%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20hospital%20must%20be%20protected.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%2C%20who%20spoke%20as%20he%20was%20signing%20a%20women's%20health%20research%20initiative%20alongside%20First%20Lady%20Jill%20Biden%2C%20added%20that%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bin%20contact%20with%20the%20Israelis%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20a%20deal%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Brelease%20of%20prisoners%26quot%3B%20was%20still%20being%20negotiated%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20Gulf%20state%20of%20Qatar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20surgeon%20with%20Doctors%20Without%20Borders%20(MSF)%2C%20the%20medical%20charity%20group%2C%20said%20that%20hundreds%20of%20people%20were%20stranded%20in%20the%20Al-Shifa%20hospital%20complex%20enduring%20%26quot%3Binhuman%26quot%3B%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20argues%20that%20its%20Hamas%20enemies%20built%20their%20military%20headquarters%20under%20the%20Al-Shifa%20hospital%20--%20a%20charge%20Hamas%20denies%20--%20while%20UN%20agencies%20and%20doctors%20in%20the%20facility%20warned%20that%20a%20lack%20of%20generator%20fuel%20was%20claiming%20lives%2C%20including%20those%20of%20infants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Health%20Organization%20in%20the%20Palestinian%20territories%20said%20early%20Monday%20that%20at%20least%202%2C300%20people%20--%20patients%2C%20health%20workers%20and%20people%20fleeing%20fighting%20--%20were%20inside%20the%20crippled%20Al-Shifa%20facility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20'Firefights'%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden's%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20Jake%20Sullivan%20later%20confirmed%20Washington%2C%20which%20has%20firmly%20backed%20Israel%20over%20its%20offensive%20against%20Hamas%2C%20had%20raised%20the%20issue%20with%20its%20ally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20want%20to%20see%20firefights%20in%20hospitals%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20a%20briefing.%20%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20see%20patients%20protected%2C%20we%20want%20to%20see%20hospitals%20protected.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20spoken%20with%20the%20Israeli%20government%20about%20this%20and%20they%20have%20said%20they%20share%20that%20view%20that%20they%20do%20not%20want%20to%20see%20firefights%20in%20hospitals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESullivan%20also%20said%20the%20United%20States%20wanted%20to%20see%20%26quot%3Bconsiderably%20longer%20pauses%20--%20days%2C%20not%20hours%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20fighting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20said%20last%20week%20that%20