%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnPray%20for%20the%20return%20of%20Kfir%2C%20his%20big%20brother%20Ariel%2C%20his%20mother%20Shiri%20and%20father%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FlyqehDslOG%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FlyqehDslOG%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Israel%20%D7%99%D7%A9%D7%A8%D7%90%D7%9C%20%F0%9F%87%AE%F0%9F%87%B1%20(%40Israel)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIsrael%2Fstatus%2F1723679340628476150%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2012%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20nine%20months%20old%2C%20Kfir%20is%20the%20youngest%20of%20the%20roughly%20240%20hostages--including%2032%20children--held%20by%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20month%20with%20no%20news%20on%20the%20family's%20whereabouts%20or%20condition%2C%20Kfir%20is%20now%2010%20months%20old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20grandfather%20clings%20to%20the%20hope%20that%20the%20family%20will%20be%20released%20soon%20amid%20reports%20of%20a%20possible%20hostage%20release%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20my%20whole%20life%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Eli%20Bibas%2C%2066%2C%20said%20Sunday%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20the%20Tazpit%20Press%20Service%20about%20his%20son%2C%20daughter-in-law%20and%20two%20grandsons%20being%20held%20by%20Hamas.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20got%20to%20get%20them%20home.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20fateful%20Saturday%2C%20Eli%20was%20supposed%20to%20visit%20the%20family%20at%2010%20a.m.%2C%20at%20their%20home%20in%20Kibbutz%20Nir%20Oz%2C%20but%20the%20air%20raid%20sirens%20went%20off%20at%206%3A30%2C%20warning%20of%20incoming%20rockets%20from%20Gaza%2C%20sending%20everybody%20to%20their%20protected%20rooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEli%2C%20who%20lives%20about%2020%20minutes%20away%2C%20texted%20Yarden%2C%2034%2C%20to%20be%20sure%20the%20family%20was%20OK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLike%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20Gaza%20border%20communities%2C%20he%20was%20in%20the%20sealed%20room%2C%26quot%3B%20Eli%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20morning%2C%20Yarden%20kept%20texting%20with%20his%20sister%20Ofri%2C%20letting%20her%20know%20what%20was%20happening%20in%20Nir%20Oz%2C%20where%20he%20lived%20with%20Shiri%2C%2032%2C%20Ariel%20and%20Kfir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20by%209%20a.m.%20the%20air%20raid%20warnings%20kept%20coming%20and%20coming%2C%20and%20Eli%20knew%20something%20was%20astray.%20At%209%3A20%20his%20son%20texted%20him%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20same%20message%20he%20sent%20his%20mom%20and%20sister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20two%20months%20earlier%2C%20Yarden's%20sister%20had%20moved%20from%20a%20nearby%20Gaza%20border%20community%20to%20the%20Golan%20Heights%2C%20to%20get%20away%20from%20the%20rocket%20attacks.%20Her%20brother%20had%20been%20thinking%20about%20making%20a%20similar%20move%2C%20his%20father%20recounted%2C%20and%20had%20also%20bought%20a%20handgun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BImagine%20what%20it%20would%20have%20been%20like%20for%20me%20now%20if%20my%20daughter%20had%20not%20moved%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20the%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYarden%20told%20his%20sister%20that%20there%20was%20noise%20outside%20and%20that%20they%20were%20having%20difficulty%20keeping%20the%20kids%20quiet%20but%20he%20was%20afraid%20to%20use%20the%20gun%20since%20the%20terrorists%20had%20automatic%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%209%3A45%20a.m.%2C%20he%20texted%2C%20%26quot%3BThey're%20inside.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%20would%20soon%20come%20out%20of%20the%20Hamas%20terrorists%20drilling%20open%20the%20front%20door.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHours%20later%2C%20a%20video%20circulated%20of%20Shiri%20holding%20both%20boys%20in%20her%20arms%2C%20a%20look%20of%20terror%20on%20her%20face%20as%20she%20was%20surrounded%20by%20terrorists%2C%20her%20boys%20facing%20her%20chest%2C%20a%20blanket%20covering%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20days%20later%2C%20another%20picture%20would%20emerge%2C%20of%20a%20bloodied%