-youngest-hostage-among-240-captured-by-hamas-4571690%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F9-month-old-israeli-baby-youngest-hostage-among-240-captured-by-hamas-4571690%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amid%20Rising%20Pollution%2C%20Parking%20Fees%20Of%20Private%20Vehicles%20Doubled%20In%20Delhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20high%20pollution%20levels%20in%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20the%20New%20Delhi%20Municipal%20Council%20(NDMC)%20has%20doubled%20the%20charges%20for%20parking%20sites%20managed%20by%20it%20to%20discourage%20people%20from%20using%20private%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20total%20of%2091%20parking%20sites%20in%20the%20NDMC%20area.%20While%2041%20of%20these%20are%20managed%20by%20the%20NDMC%2C%20the%20maintenance%20of%20others%20has%20been%20outsourced%20to%20other%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParking%20sites%20between%20Rajpath%20and%20AIIMS%2C%20including%20those%20at%20Sarojini%20Nagar%20market%2C%20Khan%20Market%2C%20Lodhi%20Road%2C%20INA%2C%20AIIMS%20and%20Safdarjung%2C%20fall%20in%20the%20NDMC%20area.%20These%20sites%20witness%20heavy%20traffic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKeeping%20in%20view%20the%20climatic%20conditions%2C%20the%20parking%20fees%20(off%20road%2Fon%20road)%20has%20been%20enhanced%20to%20twice%20the%20existing%20(amount)%20to%20discourage%20private%20transport%20for%20the%20parking%20managed%20by%20NDMC%20through%20its%20own%20staff%20till%2031st%20January%202024%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20official%20notification%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20has%20been%20taken%20keeping%20in%20view%20the%20Graded%20Action%20Response%20Plan%20(GRAP)%20Stage%20IV%20guidelines%20that%20are%20in%20place%20in%20Delhi%20owing%20to%20the%20pollution%20situation%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGRAP%2C%20the%20Central%20government's%20air%20pollution%20control%20plan%20for%20Delhi-NCR%2C%20categorises%20actions%20into%20four%20stages%3A%20Stage%20I%20-%20Poor%20(AQI%20201-300)%3B%20Stage%20II%20-%20Very%20Poor%20(AQI%20301-400)%3B%20Stage%20III%20-%20Severe%20(AQI%20401-450)%3B%20and%20Stage%20IV%20-%20Severe%20Plus%20(AQI%20above%20450).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NDMC%20presently%20charges%20Rs%2020%20per%20hour%20and%20a%20maximum%20of%20Rs%20100%20per%20day%20for%20four-wheelers%20at%20surface%20parking%20sites%20and%20Rs%2010%20per%20hour%20and%20a%20maximum%20of%20Rs%2050%20per%20day%20for%20two-wheelers.%20The%20monthly%20charges%20for%20four-wheelers%20are%20fixed%20at%20Rs%202%2C000%20and%20Rs%201%2C000%20for%20two-wheelers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20charges%20Rs%2010%20for%20up%20to%20four%20hours%20for%20four-wheelers%20and%20Rs%205%20for%20up%20to%20four%20hours%20for%20two-wheelers%20at%20its%20multilevel%20parking%20sites.%20The%20same%20rates%20apply%20at%20Palika%20underground%20parking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699898220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2015-02%2Fair-pollution-delhi_650x400_71423148405.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famid-rising-pollution-parking-fees-of-private-vehicles-doubled-in-delhi-4571723%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20high%20pollution%20levels%20in%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20the%20New%20Delhi%20Municipal%20Council%20(NDMC)%20has%20doubled%20the%20charges%20for%20parking%20sites%20managed%20by%20it%20to%20discourage%20people%20from%20using%20private%20vehicles.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famid-rising-pollution-parking-fees-of-private-vehicles-doubled-in-delhi-4571723%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famid-rising-pollution-parking-fees-of-private-vehicles-