In%20response%20to%20the%20pleas%20of%20his%20subjects%2C%20Krishna%20confronted%20Narakasura.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20fierce%20battle%2C%20Krishna%20ultimately%20vanquished%20the%20demon%2C%20liberating%20over%20a%20thousand%20captive%20women%20and%20restoring%20justice%20and%20honour.%20The%20victory%20of%20Krishna%20over%20Narakasura%20is%20celebrated%20during%20Diwali%2C%20symbolising%20the%20triumph%20of%20righteousness.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20each%20passing%20year%2C%20localities%20have%20been%20getting%20more%20and%20more%20competitive.%20In%20villages%20and%20towns%20across%20Goa%2C%20groups%20of%20young%20men%20%E2%80%93%20proudly%20labelled%20%E2%80%98the%20Pirate%20Boys%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98Sanskaari%20boys%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98Anjuna%20boyz%E2%80%99%20and%20the%20like%20%E2%80%93%20pull%20in%20funding%2C%20come%20up%20with%20a%20creative%20concept%20and%20get%20moving%20on%20getting%20materials%20together%20for%20the%20all-night%20party.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20one%20demon%20king%20with%20dreadlocks%2C%20to%20many%20more%20with%20sinewy%20muscular%20thighs%20to%20yet%20more%20with%20snake-like%20lower%20bodies%20%E2%80%93%20the%20interpretations%20are%20many.%20The%20effigies%20are%20decorated%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20ways%2C%20from%20golden%20chains%2C%20to%20whips%20made%20of%20neon%20light%20and%20even%20accomplices%20like%20the%20evil%20spirit%20from%20Hollywood%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Nun%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20competitions%20getting%20more%20intense%20and%20lively%20and%20cash%20prizes%20ranging%20from%20Rs%205%2C000%20to%20Rs%201.5%20lakh%2C%20the%20night%20before%20Diwali%20is%20spent%20in%20revelry%20on%20the%20roads%2C%20with%20locals%20and%20tourists%20alike%20stopping%20at%20various%20effigies%20to%20take%20photos%20or%20join%20in%20on%20the%20f