anga%20and%20Ma%20Yamuna%20or%20Lord%20so-and-so%20give%20answers%20for%20the%20way%20out%20of%20extinction%20to%20leaders%20whose%20policies%20have%20ruined%20the%20source%20of%20our%20holiest%20rivers%20and%20temple%20towns%20in%20unimaginable%20ways%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENature%2C%20or%20Gods%20if%20you%20will%2C%20permit%20just%20so%20much%20cheating%20and%20exploitation%20of%20natural%20resources.%20No%20more.%20It%20is%20literally%20a%20pathetic%20fallacy%20to%20say%20that%20nature%20mourns%20extinction.%20Nature%20uses%20extinction%20to%20wipe%20off%20a%20species%20that%20has%20outlived%20its%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20the%20annual%20wearing%20of%20red%20poppies%20or%20Soldiers%E2%80%99%20Day%20flags%20upon%20our%20lapels%2C%20erecting%20war%20memorials%20to%20honour%20the%20dead%2C%20or%20showering%20pilgrims%20with%20rose%20petals%20and%20performing%20smoke-emitting%20%3Cem%3Eyagna%3C%2Fem%3Es%20for%20purifying%20the%20environment%20is%20not%20going%20to%20ward%20off%20the%20next%20mass%20extinction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20hasten%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20inconvenient%20truth%2C%20but%20there%20it%20is!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fmrinal-pande%5C%22%3EMrinal%20Pande%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20writer%20and%20veteran%20journalist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699770526000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F17153905%2Fpaddy-burning1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fthe-blowing-of-toxic-winds-is-a-pattern-we-need-to-break%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20is%20an%20inconvenient%20truth%20we%20must%20confront.%20Just%20erecting%20war%20memorials%20to%20honour%20the%20dead%2C%20showering%20pilgrims%20with%20rose%20petals%20or%20performing%20smoke-emitting%20yagnas%20for%20purifying%20the%20environment%20is%20not%20going%20to%20ward%20off%20the%20next%20mass%20extinction.%20It%20may%20hasten%20it.