kh%20students%20successfully%20qualified.%20The%20exam%20preparation%20programme%20on%20the%20portal%20has%20seen%20a%20significant%20increase%20in%20student%20participation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20the%20online%20platform%20has%20received%20over%2050%2C700%20registrations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThings%20to%20know%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20NPTEL-GATE%20portal%20offers%20all%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F229119%2Fiit-madras-free-online-course-nptel-registration-date-how-to-apply-india-ros174%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efeatures%20for%20free%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBetween%20August%202022%20and%20February%202023%2C%20students%20completed%20115%20mock%20tests%20across%20six%20key%20subjects%20%E2%80%94%20electrical%20engineering%2C%20mechanical%20engineering%2C%20civil%20engineering%2C%20electronics%20and%20communication%2C%20physics%2C%20and%20chemistry.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20current%20semester%20started%20on%2015%20October%2C%202023.%20As%20part%20of%20this%2C%2019%20mock%20tests%20were%20completed%20across%20seven%20subjects%20%E2%80%94%20including%20the%20six%20mentioned%20above%20in%20addition%20to%20biotechnology.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20apply%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EParticipants%20can%20register%20using%20an%20active%20email%20ID%20and%20mobile%20number%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgate.nptel.ac.in%2Fregistration.php%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eofficial%20website%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFill%20out%20the%20online%20form%20with%20accurate%20information%20and%20upload%20all%20necessary%20documents.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20more%20information%2C%20check%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C