region%20before%20taking%20up%20the%20expansion%20of%20NH%20163%20between%20Hyderabad%20and%20Bijapur%2C%20which%20passes%20through%20Chevella%20in%20Ranga%20Reddy%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20citizens%E2%80%99%20group%20has%20welcomed%20the%20NGT%E2%80%99s%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECitizens%20vs%20NHAI%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20mid-2019%2C%20the%20members%20of%20this%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F312765%2Fhow-to-start-plantation-drive-in-my-city-kolkata-engineer-shares-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecitizens%E2%80%99%20group%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20supported%20by%20around%20300%20individuals%2C%20were%20informed%20that%20about%201%2C000%20banyan%20trees%20were%20to%20be%20chopped%20off%20or%20translocated%20for%20the%20road%20widening%20project.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20no%20one%20who%20intended%20to%20speak%20against%20this%20decision.%20This%20is%20when%20we%20decided%20to%20get%20together%20and%20take%20action%2C%E2%80%9D%20Asiya%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20found%20that%20the%20authorities%20could%20easily%20chop%20off%20trees%20in%20the%20name%20of%20developmental%20project%2C%20and%20there%20was%20no%20law%20to%20protect%20them.%20However%2C%20we%20found%20a%20loophole.%20The%20NHAI%20did%20not%20conduct%20the%20EIA%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Environment%20Protection%20Act%201986%20mandates%20an%20Environmental%20Impact%20Assessment%20(EIA)%20to%20assess%20damage%20in%20the%20development%20projects%20and%20provide%20a%20plan%20to%20reduce%20the%20negative%20environmental%20effect%20of%20proposed%20development%20projects%20through%20alternative%20approaches%20and%20design%20modification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-6-1699538732.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%202019%2C%20a%20group%20of%20about%2020%20citizens%20got%20together%20to%20fight%20the%20authorities%20to%20save%20their%20beloved%20trees.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-6-1699538732.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-6-1699538732-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-6-1699538732-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-6-1699538732-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-6-1699538732-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333948%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%202019%2C%20a%20group%20of%20about%2020%20citizens%20got%20together%20to%20fight%20the%20authorities%20to%20save%20their%20beloved%20trees.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20NH%20163%20widening%20project%2C%20the%20NHAI%20did%20not%20look%20into%20alternative%20routes%20and%20conduct%20an%20enumeration%20of%20the%20trees%20affected%2C%20despite%20awarding%20contracts%20for%20developing%20the%20road.%20The%20old%20road%2C%20with%20thousands%20of%20trees%20including%20banyans%20planted%20by%20Nizam%E2%80%99s%20government%2C%20has%20a%20heritage%20value%2C%E2%80%9D%20points%20out%20Natasha%20Ramarathnam%2C%20one%20of%20the%20members%20of%20the%20citizens%E2%80%99%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20banyans%20form%20an%20ecological%20corridor%20connecting%20different%20parts%20of%20Telangana%20state%20for%20many%20birds%20and%20other%20species.%20Neither%20the%20unique%20features%20of%20this%20corridor%20nor%20its%20historic%20value%20were%20addressed.%20In%20an%20era%20of%20climate%20change%2C%20we%20must%20reevaluate%20what%20it%20means%20to%20cut%20down%20trees%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20thousands%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20EIA%20is%20usually%20required%20for%20a%20development%20project%20when%20there%20are%20protected%20areas%20like%20national%20parks%2C%20wildlife%20sanctuaries%2C%20and%20biosphere%20reserves%20in%20the%20project%20area%20of%20influence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20applicants%20in%20the%20NGT%20petition%2C%20Tejah%20Balantrapu%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20realised%20that%20trees%20have%20a%20legal%20value%20if%20they%20form%20forests%20and%20reserves%2C%20but%20trees%20lined%20around%20the%20road%20do%20not%20have%20such%20value.%20Essentially%2C%20all%20these%20natural%20landforms%20%E2%80%94%20trees%2C%20rocks%2C%20boulders%2C%20and%20water%20bodies%20%E2%80%94%20are%20looked%20at%20as%20obstacles%20in%20the%20way%20of%20expansion.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20reason%2C%20the%2043-year-old%20says%2C%20why%20NHAI%20said%20EIA%20was%20not%20required%20in%20this%20particular%20project.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20said%20that%20EIA%20needed%20to%20be%20conducted%20only%20for%20highway%20projects%20longer%20than%20100%20km.%20And%20since%20this%20stretch%20was%20below%20100%20km%20(46%20km)%2C%20it%20did%20not%20require%20an%20EIA.%20However%2C%20NH-163%20has%20been%20expanded%20before%2C%20again%20in%20small%20stretches%2C%20from%20Warangal%20to%20Hyderabad.%20As%20a%20result%20of%20this%20segmentation%2C%20the%20full%20length%20of%20the%20highway%20escapes%20the%20rule%20of%20assessment%20for%20impact%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20as%20per%20Indian%20Road%20Congress%20(IRC)%20guidelines%2C%20NHAI%20needs%20to%20incorporate%20natural%20landscape%20in%20road%20design.%20Besides%2C%20these%20banyan%20trees%20in%20thousands%20act%20as%20a%20corridor%20for%20several%20