46.6%20km%20stretch%2C%20which%20was%20lower%20than%20what%20the%20authorities%20quoted%20(749)%2C%20informs%20Natasha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20this%20database%2C%20we%20could%20counter%20the%20claims%20of%20NHAI%20that%20these%20were%20very%20small%20and%20stunted%20trees%20and%20it%20would%20be%20no%20loss%20if%20they%20were%20axed.%20What%20we%20took%20to%20NGT%20was%20not%20just%20an%20emotional%20appeal%20but%20actually%20data%20backed%20with%20facts%20and%20figures.%20Also%2C%20anyone%20can%20replicate%20this%20method%20with%20little%20effort%20to%20geo-tag%20trees%20in%20their%20cities%20and%20hold%20authorities%20accountable%20when%20healthy%20trees%20are%20made%20to%20disappear%20overnight%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20citizens%E2%80%99%20group%20also%20sought%20help%20from%20several%20ministers%2C%20Members%20of%20Parliament%20(MPs)%2C%20and%20Members%20of%20the%20Legislative%20Assembly%20(MLAs)%2C%20Asiya%20says.%20But%20when%20no%20one%20in%20power%20listened%20to%20them%2C%20they%20approached%20the%20National%20Green%20Tribunal%20and%20filed%20a%20petition%20against%20the%20decision%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20three%20citizens%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Natasha%2C%20Pranay%20Juvvadi%2C%20and%20Tejah%20%E2%80%94%20became%20applicants%20in%20the%20case%2C%20the%20remaining%20citizens%20kept%20organising%20awareness%20campaigns%20across%20the%20city%20to%20make%20authorities%20understand%20why%20there%20was%20a%20need%20to%20save%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F138262%2Fpillalamarri-mahabubnagar-telengana-banyan-tree%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egiant%20trees%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-4-1-1699537213.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20recent%20decision%20by%20the%20National%20Green%20Tribunal%20is%20a%20big%20win%20for%20citizens.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-4-1-1699537213.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-4-1-1699537213-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-4-1-1699537213-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-4-1-1699537213-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-4-1-1699537213-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333927%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20recent%20decision%20by%20the%20National%20Green%20Tribunal%20is%20a%20big%20win%20for%20the%20citizens.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20on%207%20November%202023%2C%20the%20NGT%20directed%20the%20NHAI%20to%20conduct%20an%20EIA.%20The%20NGT%20has%20also%20directed%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Environment%20and%20Forests%20to%20issue%20the%20Terms%20of%20Reference%20(ToR)%20at%20the%20earliest%20and%20complete%20the%20process%20within%20four%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20welcome%20the%20decision%2C%20but%20the%20battle%20is%20not%20won%20yet.%20It%20is%20a%20small%20victory%20but%20we%20are%20not%20being%20complacent%20about%20it.%20We%20do%20not%20know%20the%20kind%20of%20report%20NHAI%20will%20come%20up%20with%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Asiya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20fight%20authorities%20as%20individuals%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETejah%20adds%20that%20the%20judgment%20is%20unique%20and%20will%20be%20exemplary%20for%20people%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20started%2C%20we%20did%20not%20have%20any%20such%20examples%20where%20people%20rose%20against%20the%20authorities%20to%20protect%20natural%20landforms.%20Others%20can%20use%20this%20judgement%20as%20a%20precedent%20which%20was%20not%20an%20option%20for%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20their%20experiences%2C%20Tejah%20also%20shares%20five%20tips%20on%20how%20to%20fight%20for%20public%20and%20natural%20properties%20as%20individuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1)%20Come%20together%20as%20a%20group%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Tejah%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20a%20big%20non-profit%20organisation%20or%20any%20powerful%20agency%2C%20we%20are%20just%20a%20group%20of%20citizens.%20The%20reason%20why%20we%20won%20is%20that%20we%20picked%20a%20specific%20issue%2C%20came%20together%2C%20and%20fought%20the%20case%20to%20the%20very%20end.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEngage%20people%20from%20across%20diverse%20cultures%2C%20backgrounds%2C%20and%20age%20groups.%20Build%20a%20group%20that%20is%20as%20broad%20as%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-5-1-1699537320.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20banyans%20form%20an%20ecological%20corridor%20connecting%20different%20parts%20of%20Telangana%20state%20for%20many%20birds%20and%20other%20species.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-5-1-1699537320.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-5-1-1699537320-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-5-1-1699537320-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-5-1-1699537320-768x402.jpg%20768w%