0others%20to%20follow%20at%20a%20time%20when%20it%20was%20unheard%20of.%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20female%20engineer%2C%20A%20Lalitha%2C%20lost%20her%20husband%20at%20a%20young%20age.%20At%20the%20first%20international%20conference%20of%20female%20engineers%20and%20scientists%20in%201964%2C%20in%20New%20York%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAbout%20150%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20would%20have%20been%20burned%20at%20the%20funeral%20pyre%20with%20my%20husband%E2%80%99s%20body.%E2%80%9D%20She%20was%20referring%20to%20the%20practice%20of%20%3Cem%3Esati%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20prevailed%20in%20India%20at%20the%20time.%20But%20instead%20of%20giving%20in%20to%20the%20societal%20standards%20set%20for%20women%20back%20then%2C%20Lalitha%20chose%20to%20defy%20the%20odds%20much%20like%20her%20compatriots.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20their%20courageous%20stories%20of%20zeal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20Ayyalasomayajula%20Lalitha%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20age%20of%2018%2C%20Lalitha%20was%20left%20to%20care%20for%20her%20four-month-old%20daughter%20following%20the%20death%20of%20her%20husband.%20For%20no%20fault%20of%20her%20own%2C%20society%20prescribed%20her%20a%20sentence%20of%20isolation.%20But%20Lalitha%20did%20not%20let%20this%20define%20her%20life%20or%20her%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332994%2Fshraddha-gaikwad-pune-security-guard-daughter-won-gold-in-skateboarding-national-level%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecareer%20choices%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20her%20daughter%2C%20Syamala%20Chenulu%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20my%20father%20passed%20away%2C%20my%20mother%20had%20to%20suffer%20more%20than%20she%20should%20have.%20Her%20mother-in-law%20had%20lost%20her%2016th%20child%20and%20took%20out%20that%20frustration%20on%20the%20young%20widow.%20It%20was%20a%20coping%20mechanism%20and%20today%2C%20I%20understand%20what%20she%20was%20going%20through.%20However%2C%20my%20mother%20decided%20not%20to%20succumb%20to%20societal%20pressures.%20She%20educated%20herself%20and%20earned%20a%20respectable%20job.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20Lalitha%20chose%20the%20engineering%20path%20in%201940%2C%20she%20was%20the%20only%20female%20among%20hundreds%20of%20boys%20at%20the%20college.%20But%20she%20was%20soon%20joined%20by%20two%20other%20women%2C%20PK%20Thresia%20and%20Leelamma%20George%20Koshie%2C%20who%20also%20carved%20out%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332094%2Frajasthan-rubi-pareek-doubles-profit-with-organic-farming-gives-free-training%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincredible%20niches%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20themselves%20in%20the%20male-dominated%20profession.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20PK%20Thresia%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20Lalitha%20expressed%20her%20wish%20to%20join%20the%20four-year%20engineering%20program%20at%20the%20College%20of%20Engineering%2C%20Guindy%2C%20University%20of%20Madras%2C%20her%20father%20who%20was%20a%20professor%20at%20the%20college%20did%20everything%20to%20support%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20getting%20admitted%20to%20the%20program%20was%20the%20least%20of%20her%20worries%20as%20Lalitha%20eventually%20discovered.%20Women%20were%20not%20welcome%20in%20a%20field%20like%20engineering.%20Intent%20to%20make%20his%20daughter%20feel%20at%20ease%2C%20her%20father%20put%20out%20an%20ad%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331809%2Fprachi-thakur-phd-iit-roorkee-achieving-success-from-a-small-town%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eother%20girls%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20also%20wished%20to%20join%20the%20program.%20Two%20women%20took%20the%20opportunity%20%E2%80%93%20PK%20Thresia%20and%20Leelamma%20George%20Koshie.%C2%A0%C2%A0